<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Legacy Home &amp; Respite Care Foundation — Caregiver Wellness &amp; Resource Hub</title>
<meta name="description" content="Supporting caregivers of loved ones with dementia — wellness grants, free respite care, events, and resources. Demo preview.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="demo-banner"><strong>DEMO PREVIEW</strong> · sample data only · built by X-Centric as a working preview for Legacy Home &amp; Respite Care Foundation</div>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a class="brand" href="index.html">
      <div class="brand-mark">L</div>
      <div class="brand-name">Legacy<small>Home &amp; Respite Care Foundation</small></div>
    </a>
    <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Menu" onclick="document.querySelector('.main-nav').classList.toggle('open')">☰</button>
    <nav class="main-nav">
      <a href="index.html" class="active">Home</a>
      <a href="about.html">About</a>
      <a href="programs.html">The Sanctuary</a>
      <a href="resources.html">Resource Hub</a>
      <a href="events.html">Events</a>
      <a href="portal.html" class="nav-portal">Caregiver Portal</a>
      <a href="#donate" class="nav-cta">Donate</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Caring for the people who care for everyone else.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Home of <strong>The Caregiver Sanctuary</strong> — a free membership community for caregivers of loved ones with dementia. Wellness grants, Memory Socials, support groups, and a place to breathe. Because your journey matters too.</p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a href="programs.html" class="btn btn-coral">Explore The Sanctuary</a>
      <a href="resources.html" class="btn btn-outline-light">Visit the Resource Hub</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="stats-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">200+</div><div class="label">Sanctuary members</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">$48K</div><div class="label">Wellness grants awarded</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">1,100</div><div class="label">Hours of drop-in respite</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">36</div><div class="label">Memory Socials &amp; events hosted</div></div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center small muted mt-16">Sample figures for demo purposes.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">What we do</span>
      <h2>Support for every step of the caregiving journey</h2>
      <p>Founded from lived experience caring for a mother with younger-onset dementia, Legacy exists to be the support we wish we'd had.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">🌱</div>
        <h3>Wellness Grants</h3>
        <p>Personalized stipends for Sanctuary members — a massage, counseling, a gym membership — each with its own care package. Because you can't pour from an empty cup.</p>
        <a class="more" href="programs.html#grants">Learn about grants →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">🏡</div>
        <h3>Memory Socials</h3>
        <p>Drop-in respite: welcoming, supervised gatherings for your loved one — familiar activities, trained staff, no pressure — while you step away and breathe.</p>
        <a class="more" href="programs.html#socials">About Memory Socials →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">🤝</div>
        <h3>Support Group &amp; Events</h3>
        <p>Our Alzheimer's Association-certified Virtual Support Group meets every Wednesday, alongside Memory Social Caregiver Events for wellness, connection, and education.</p>
        <a class="more" href="events.html">See upcoming events →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Upcoming</span>
        <h2 style="font-size: 30px; margin-bottom: 18px;">Join us this month</h2>
{%- for ev in events if ev.teaser %}
        <div class="card event-card{% if not loop.last %} mb-16{% endif %}">
          <div class="event-date"><div class="month">{{ ev.month | e }}</div><div class="day">{{ ev.day | e }}</div></div>
          <div>
            <span class="badge {{ ev.badge_class }}">{{ ev.badge | e }}</span>
            <h3 style="font-size: 18px; margin: 8px 0 4px;">{{ ev.title | e }}</h3>
            <div class="event-meta">{{ ev.meta | e }}</div>
            <a class="more" href="events.html">Register →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
{%- endfor %}
        <a href="events.html" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm mt-24" style="display:inline-block;">All events</a>
      </div>
      <div class="visual">
        <span class="eyebrow">One record, every program</span>
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 12px;">A hub that knows your caregivers</h3>
        <p class="muted small mb-16">Behind this site is a single caregiver record — events attended, grants in progress, respite used, follow-ups needed. No more scattered spreadsheets.</p>
        <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
          <h4>Maria G. — Sanctuary member since 2024</h4>
          <div class="kv-row"><span class="k">Wellness grant</span><span class="v"><span class="badge badge-amber">In review</span></span></div>
          <div class="kv-row"><span class="k">Last attended</span><span class="v">Virtual Support Group · Jun 24</span></div>
          <div class="kv-row"><span class="k">Memory Socials</span><span class="v">4 attended · 2026</span></div>
          <div class="kv-row"><span class="k">Follow-up</span><span class="v">Grant check-in · this week</span></div>
        </div>
        <p class="small muted mt-8">Sample record — demo data.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding: 48px 0; background: var(--plum-dark);">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--coral);">Free membership</span>
    <h2 style="color: #fff; margin-bottom: 12px;">Join The Caregiver Sanctuary</h2>
    <p style="color: #ecd9cd; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 24px;">A free membership community for caregivers of loved ones living with dementia — support groups, wellness grants, Memory Socials, and events, all in one place.</p>
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-coral" onclick="openMembership(); return false;">Become a member — free</a>
  </div>
</section>

{% include '_membership-modal.html.j2' %}
<section id="donate" style="background: var(--sand);">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <span class="eyebrow">Support the mission</span>
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 14px;">Every gift gives a caregiver room to breathe</h2>
    <p class="muted" style="max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto 28px;">Your donation funds wellness grants, free respite hours, and community programs for family caregivers across our region.</p>
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-coral" onclick="alert('Demo: this connects to Legacy\'s existing GiveButter donation page.'); return false;">Donate via GiveButter</a>
    <p class="small muted mt-16">Donations continue to run through GiveButter — already set up, kept as-is.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div>
        <h4>Legacy Home &amp; Respite Care Foundation</h4>
        <p style="font-size: 13.5px; max-width: 300px;">A nonprofit supporting caregivers of loved ones with dementia — wellness, respite, and community since 2023.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>The Sanctuary</h4>
        <a href="programs.html#grants">Wellness Grants</a>
        <a href="programs.html#socials">Memory Socials</a>
        <a href="events.html">Support Group &amp; Events</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Get Involved</h4>
        <a href="request-support.html">Request Support</a>
        <a href="#" onclick="alert('Demo: partner/volunteer intake form — routes into the caregiver record system.'); return false;">Volunteer</a>
        <a href="#" onclick="alert('Demo: organizational partnership form.'); return false;">Partner with us</a>
        <a href="index.html#donate">Donate</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Access</h4>
        <a href="portal.html">Caregiver Portal</a>
        <a href="staff.html">Staff Console (demo)</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <span>© 2026 Legacy Home &amp; Respite Care Foundation · Demo preview — sample data only</span>
      <span>Built &amp; hosted by X-Centric · Managed Hosted Hub</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
